Dapo Abiodun is winner of Ogun State APC governorship primaries The National Working Committee (NWC) of the All Progressives Congress (APC) announces Mr. Dapo Abiodun as winner of the Party’s Ogun State governorship primaries. Abiodun won the Primary Election after scoring 102,305 votes. Other aspirants scored the following: Jimi Lawal -51,153
Kunle Akinlade – 23, 443
Bimbo Ashiru – 29, 764
Senator Adegbenga Kaka – 17, 771
Abayomi Semako Koroto – 9, 610 SIGNED: *Mr. Yekini Nabena*
Ag. National Publicity Secretary